emuInput.TitMainTitle: Rev. Patrick LeRoy and Murrel Wynn Jones dancing in ballroom of Hotel Webster Hall for Holy Cross Episcopal Church's 50th Anniversary Dinner Dance
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 22, 1967, pg. 13, reads: "Work-Out - The crowd got a kick out of watching the Rev. LeRoy Patrick and Muriel [Murrel] Wynn Jones good-naturedly "work-out" on a number."
